invalid type: string "Issue: Network outage affecting whole street\nDescription: Multiple customers on the same street report total loss of service since 6 am.\nResolution: Major fibre backhaul cut reported by the field team at a junction box 2 km from the affected area. Repair crew dispatched; ETA 4 hours. Affected customers sent proactive SMS update. Service restored after 3 hours 20 minutes."˙˙